# Fansly Media Downloader

A simple Chrome extension that provides easy access to media content from Fansly with one-click convenience.

## What It Does

This extension adds convenient download buttons to Fansly pages that appear automatically when media is detected:

- **Instant image downloads** with a single click
- **Direct access to video files** in new tabs
- **Separate audio track access** when available
- **Combined video+audio option** for complete media

## Features

- 🟢 **One-Click Image Download** - Download images instantly without extra steps
- 🔴 **Video File Access** - Get direct access to video files in new tabs
- 🔵 **Audio Track Access** - Access separate audio tracks when available
- 🟣 **Complete Media Access** - Open both video and audio simultaneously
- 🎯 **Smart Detection** - Buttons appear automatically when media is available
- 📱 **Non-Intrusive** - Clean overlay that doesn't interfere with browsing
- 🔒 **Privacy Safe** - Works entirely locally in your browser

## Installation

1. Download this repository as a ZIP file and extract it
2. Open Chrome and navigate to `chrome://extensions/`
3. Enable "Developer mode" in the top-right corner
4. Click "Load unpacked" and select the extracted folder
5. The extension is now ready to use on Fansly

## Usage

### Downloading Images
- Visit any Fansly page with images
- Click the green "Download Image" button that appears
- The image downloads instantly to your computer

### Accessing Videos & Audio
- Go to any Fansly video post and play the video
- Use the colored buttons that appear:
  - **Red button** - Opens the video file in a new tab
  - **Blue button** - Opens the audio track in a new tab
  - **Purple button** - Opens both video and audio in separate tabs
- In the new tabs, use your browser's save function to download

## Button Reference

| Button | Color | Action |
|--------|-------|--------|
| ⬇️ Download Image | Green | Direct image download |
| 🎥 Open Video | Red | Opens video file in new tab |
| 🎵 Open Audio | Blue | Opens audio track in new tab |
| 📹 Open Video+Audio | Purple | Opens both files in separate tabs |

## Important Notes

### Legal Compliance
- Respect content creators' rights and copyrights
- Follow Fansly's Terms of Service
- Use content responsibly and legally
- This tool is for personal use only

### Privacy Assurance
- No data collection or tracking
- No external server communication
- All processing happens locally in your browser
- Only activates on Fansly websites

## Support

If you experience any issues:
- Ensure you're on a supported Fansly page
- Play videos completely to enable detection
- Refresh the page if buttons don't appear
- Check that the extension is enabled in Chrome

